law.catch_line: This Part III of this subtitle does not affect or change the law applicable to:...
law.text:
This Part III of this subtitle does not affect or change the law applicable to:
an accidental personal injury or occupational disease that occurred before the provisions of this Part III of this subtitle became effective; or
an individual eligible for benefits as the result of accidental personal injury or occupational disease that occurred when a different rate or percentage payment basis was in effect.
